libs.content:
find_library(freetype_lib
	names ${_freetype_libraries} freetype libfreetype
	hints
		env freetypepath32
		env freetypepath
		env freetype_dir
		env depspath32
		env depspath
		${freetypepath32}
		${freetypepath}
		${depspath32}
		${depspath}
		${_freetype_library_dirs}
	paths
		/usr/lib /usr/local/lib /opt/local/lib /sw/lib
	path_suffixes
		lib32 lib
		libs32 libs
		bin32 bin
		../lib32 ../lib
		../libs32 ../libs
		../bin32 ../bin)

find_library(ffmpeg_${component}_library
		names
			"${component}" "lib${component}"
		hints
			env ffmpegpath32
			env ffmpegpath
			env depspath32
			env depspath
			${ffmpegpath32}
			${ffmpegpath}
			${depspath32}
			${depspath}
			${pc_ffmpeg_${component}_library_dirs}
		path_suffixes
			lib32 lib
			libs32 libs
			bin32 bin
			../lib32 ../lib
			../libs32 ../libs
			../bin32 ../bin)

      doc           "the sphinx-${_sphinx_tool} python script."
